Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.name: scaleToFill
Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.abstract: The option to scale the content to fit the size of itself by changing the aspect ratio of the content if necessary.

Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.name: scaleAspectFit
Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.abstract: The option to scale the content to fit the size of the view by maintaining the aspect ratio.

Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.name: scaleAspectFill
Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.abstract: The option to scale the content to fill the size of the view. Some portion of the content may be clipped to fill the view’s bounds.

Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.name: center
Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.abstract: The option to center the content in the view’s bounds, keeping the proportions the same.

Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.name: top
Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.abstract: The option to center the content aligned at the top in the view’s bounds.

Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.name: bottom
Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.abstract: The option to center the content aligned at the bottom in the view’s bounds.

Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.name: left
Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.abstract: The option to align the content on the left of the view.

Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.name: right
Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.abstract: The option to align the content on the right of the view.

Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.name: topLeft
Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.abstract: The option to align the content in the top-left corner of the view.

Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.name: topRight
Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.abstract: The option to align the content in the top-right corner of the view.

Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.name: bottomLeft
Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.abstract: The option to align the content in the bottom-left corner of the view.

Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.name: bottomRight
Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html#/s:5TPS.abstract: The option to align the content in the bottom-right corner of the view.

Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html.name: TPSVGImageContentMode
Enums/TPSVGImageContentMode.html.abstract: A flag used to determine how an SVG image is layed out in its bounds.

Classes/TPSVG.html#/s:5TPSVGAAC10content.name: init(contentsOf:)
Classes/TPSVG.html#/s:5TPSVGAAC10content.abstract: Initialize a TPSVG with the contents of a URL.

Classes/TPSVG.html#/s:5TPSVGAAC3rawABSS_.name: init(raw:)
Classes/TPSVG.html#/s:5TPSVGAAC3rawABSS_.abstract: Initalizes a TPSVG with the given raw SVG string.

Classes/TPSVG.html#/s:5TPSVGAAC4dataAB10.name: init(data:)
Classes/TPSVG.html#/s:5TPSVGAAC4dataAB10.abstract: Initializes a TPSVG with the parsed UTF-8 raw string of data.

Classes/TPSVG.html.name: TPSVG
Classes/TPSVG.html.abstract: TPSVG is the main class to parse an SVG file.
